or if somebody converted into a product, that's Salesforce.

00:45:34.280 --> 00:45:37.280
So, it really depends on what you're trying to accomplish.

00:45:37.280 --> 00:45:42.280
Both, one thing they both have in common, right, they are platforms.

00:45:43.280 --> 00:45:46.280
They integrate into your data.

