00:48:01.280 --> 00:48:07.280
That made them wildly more likely to join our platform and become a driver.

00:48:07.280 --> 00:48:17.280
And so I think that like really the insight there is that try to think about how people can be similar as much as they are different.

00:48:17.280 --> 00:48:23.280
And that people understand value based upon something that they can relate to.

00:48:24.280 --> 00:48:47.280
So for example, if you think about asking someone to do something in your marketing funnel, meaning like say make a purchase, if you present them with something that is very, appears to be very low value, like if you were buying Zoom and it was 99 cents, that's probably going to harm your conversion rate because it doesn't look like it has very much value.

00:48:47.280 --> 00:48:50.280
Anything that's a dollar doesn't have any value.

00:48:50.280 --> 00:48:56.280
Start valuing your products the way that people would perceive that value.

00:48:56.280 --> 00:49:07.280
